### 1. GET all tasks
# Expected: 200 OK with an array containing the initial 2 tasks
GET cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. GET a single task
# Expected: 200 OK with the task object for ID 1
GET cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. GET a task that doesn't exist
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks/999
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. POST a new task (valid data)
# Expected: 201 Created with the new task object (ID should be 3)
POST cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Complete Assignment 1",
    "description": "Finalize the Flask API extensions",
    "user_id": 1,
    "completed": false
}

###

### 5. POST a task with missing title
# Expected: 400 Bad Request
POST cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "description": "This request is missing the required title field"
}

###

### 6. POST a task with invalid user_id
# Expected: 400 Bad Request (User 999 does not exist)
POST cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Ghost Task",
    "user_id": 999,
    "completed": false
}

###

### 7. PUT to update a task
# Expected: 200 OK with the updated task object
PUT cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Learn REST (Updated)",
    "completed": false
}

###

### 8. DELETE a task
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/tasks/2

###

### 9. GET tasks for a specific user
# Expected: 200 OK with an array of tasks belonging to User 1
GET cst8916-rest-api-demo-h2d3f2hpadb3gmbp.canadacentral-01.azurewebsites.net/users/1/tasks
Accept: application/json